{"type":"message","id":"1e6d9c3a","parentId":"40e55ce6","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:04:05.651Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only active session is the cron job itself. The last message in the session is the assistant's own message (the cron job's thinking). This means there are no recent user messages in the last 5 minutes. The sessions_list shows only one session which is the cron job session itself. The last user message would be from 5 minutes ago... wait, let me re-check. The updatedAt is 1775077429566 which is the session update time. The cron job just started, so there's no actual user message in the last 5 minutes.\n\nActually, looking more carefully, this session is the cron job itself - it's asking me to check if there are active conversations with real users. The sessions_list is showing me the cron session, but I need to check if there are OTHER sessions with recent user activity. The `activeMinutes: 5` filter should show sessions with activity in the last 5 minutes. The only session returned is the cron job itself.\n\nWait - the cron job is running in the main session, so the `sessions_list` with `activeMinutes: 5` would include the main session if it had recent activity. But the only session returned is the cron job session labeled \"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习\". \n\nThis cron job seems to be triggered in the main session. \n\nSince the sessions_list only returns the cron job itself with no other active user sessions, I should proceed with the autonomous learning task. I'll search for recent industry trends and developments relevant to Dao Jian Network's operations.","thinkingSignature":"2373587ee4ad83004b7d9c7890f0d843b6584e8b0bc2d8739d720bef4bfe27d1"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前只有 cron 任务会话本身，没有其他用户活跃对话。执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ociqu2uwltdc_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":851,"output":374,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45206,"cost":{"input":0.00025529999999999997,"output":0.00044879999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00202353}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775077434596}}
{"type":"message","id":"8d250ce3","parentId":"1e6d9c3a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:04:05.657Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ociqu2uwltdc_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775077445654}}
{"type":"message","id":"35d0f87c","parentId":"8d250ce3","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:04:11.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll search for the latest information on relevant industries. Let me search for multiple topics and then compile the results.","thinkingSignature":"ce9730924b6dbbdb1fd8a63d5f1bcf48e712fa6de4a9f8b690f75341882a0e09"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t9fdfu21cdr1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型发展趋势 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t9fdfu21cdr1_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t9fdfu21cdr1_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务行业趋势 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t9fdfu21cdr1_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成项目案例 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1740,"output":252,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45973,"cost":{"input":0.000522,"output":0.0003024,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0021438299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775077445657}}
